content: hello my fellow crocheters i hope you like this keychain tutorial this is a very easy no sew pattern that works up fast this is a great option if you are looking for some easy patterns to stock up for markets you may sell the items made using this pattern but please credit me as the designer do share your pics with me on instagram by tagging @madewithlovebydaisy if you have any questions regarding the pattern do reach out to me daisy
